29 SUMMARY
3300 This amendment removes the transfer language from the bill and replaces it with an
3311 appropriations and allocations section that deappropriates funds from the Mental Health
3322 Services - Community program in the Department of Health and Human Services and
3333 appropriates and allocates funds to the Medical Care - Payments to Providers program in
3344 the Department of Health and Human Services.
